description:
Define all TypeScript interfaces used across the monorepo in libs/shared/src/lib/types.ts. No logic — types only.

Types to define:
- LoginEntry: { id, type: 'login', title, url, username, password, notes, createdAt, updatedAt }
- SecureNoteEntry: { id, type: 'note', title, body, createdAt, updatedAt }
- VaultEntry = LoginEntry | SecureNoteEntry
- NewEntry = Omit<VaultEntry, 'id' | 'createdAt' | 'updatedAt'>
- EncryptedVault: { version, kdf, salt, iv, ciphertext, hint }
- VaultRequest discriminated union (SETUP, UNLOCK, LOCK, GET_STATUS, GET_ENTRIES, ADD_ENTRY, UPDATE_ENTRY, DELETE_ENTRY)
- VaultResponse discriminated union (OK, STATUS, ENTRIES, ERROR, LOCKED)

Update libs/shared/src/index.ts to re-export all types.
